                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940430-113-off625 t17940430-113-crimeloc627"></join>, at the corner of Shoe-lane, I was going along, and Thomas Davis put his hand into my pocket, and picked it out, Mr. Hart see him do it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17940430-113-person1143">
                  THOMAS
                   HART
